attributes.MarketingDescription: <b>Bitty Twins</b></br></br>Delight your little one with a Bitty Baby to cuddle and love—and treasure for years to come. The Bitty Baby doll is 15" tall, with eyes that open and close. She has a cuddly cloth body, and her head and limbs are made of smooth vinyl. Bitty Baby arrives dressed in a diaper and a pink bodysuit, and comes with a choice of sleeper. You can create a <a href="http://play.americangirl.com/play/bitty/popups/welcomebittybaby/index.html" target="_blank">personalized welcome announcement</a> as a keepsake, too.
attributes.AwardWinners: <strong><font color="#E21776">#1 on Parents’ roundup of “12 Best Baby Dolls of 2016"</font></strong>
